<li><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096148/" class="external text" title="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096148/" rel="nofollow">"Souvenir"</a> - a movie based on the events at Oradour-sur-Glane</li>
<li><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0073864/" class="external text" title="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0073864/" rel="nofollow">Le Vieux Fusil</a> - another movie based on these events</li>
<li><a href="http://www.oradour.info/ruined/chapter2.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.oradour.info/ruined/chapter2.htm" rel="nofollow">Account containing witness testimony</a></li>
</ul>


